## Privacy policy

This is the privacy policy for the RGR FM Player android application.

### Data collaction

This application does not collect any personally identifiable information or any other data. All data set by the user, e.g. application preferences, are stored on your device only, and can be simply erased by clearing the applications's data or uninstalling it.
This application is not responsible for the privacy policy of any webiste or application that the user might be navigated to when clicking on the social media buttons. Always read and review the desitinations privacy policy.

### Android permissions required by the application

The list of permissions required by the app are:

| Permission | Why it is required |
| :---: | --- |
| `android.permission.INTERNET` | Required to access the RGR FM music stream and playist information from www.rgrfm.be |
| `android.permission.WAKE_LOCK` | Required to keep the application and thus the music stream running when when the screen is turned off. |
| `android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE` | Enables the app to kep the music stream running when the app is in the background. |

### Contact

If you have any concerns or questions about the application or the privacy policy, then you can contect us at corncobsapps@gmail.com
